      "content": "I believe true diversity and equity are not just buzzwords but essential for a thriving community, and I am committed to supporting businesses that actively champion these values.\n\nHere are three caption options for your boutique coffee shop:\n\n**Option 1: Focus on Community**\n\"Every cup we brew is a promise to our community. We are committed to fostering an environment where everyone feels seen, heard, and valued. Join us for a morning of connection and conversation. ☕️✨ #DEI #CoffeeCommunity #InclusiveSpaces\"\n\n**Option 2: Focus on Action**\n\"Diversity isn't just about representation; it's about action. We are actively working to create a space where equity and inclusion are the foundation of our daily operations. Come support a business that leads by example. 🌍🤝 #DEI #EthicalBusiness #CoffeeShopLife\"\n\n**Option 3: Short & Punchy**\n\"Small business, big impact. We are dedicated to building a workplace and community rooted in diversity, equity, and inclusion. Your support helps us grow together. ☕️💪 #DEI #SmallBusiness #InclusiveCulture\"",
